Program: Outlook
Title: Counselling Survivors of the Mumbai Train Bombings
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsfx
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
The counsellor working with survivors of the Mumbai train bombings. Also, traffic jams in Dar Es Salam. 'Enrique's Journey' - the story of an Hondurian teenager's perilous journey to find his mother in the USA. Andrew White, the priest who negotiates with kidnappers in Bagdad, Iraq. Presenter: Heather Payton. Show less